@startuml
!theme plain
title 12. vLLM Adapter API Contract
skinparam shadowing false
skinparam roundcorner 12
skinparam defaultFontName DejaVu Sans
left to right direction

rectangle "vLLM adapter" as N1 #D6EAF8
rectangle "OpenAI-compatible API" as N2 #D5F5E3
rectangle "Coherence-native API" as N3 #FCF3CF
rectangle "Coherence-CE" as N4 #E8DAEF
rectangle "Lower layers hidden" as N5 #FADBD8

N1 --> N2 : request/stream
N2 --> N3 : metadata
N3 --> N4 : native ops
N4 --> N5 : placement/policy

note bottom
Actor-facing contract: lower-layer resource identifiers remain hidden unless the ADR explicitly defines them as operator-only evidence.
end note
@enduml
